{"width":3000,"height":1688,"file_path":"/42Ym2pktNs6ff9qmVPruOGZd6Ru.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1723,"height":969,"file_path":"/8a8oxKfvAl7q295Hcsi2Cd5yv4S.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/geEQPJt3lJ7pZJ8nkJDIQefCNsK.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/fYdAFm1SYyq8uRqBeFKuLH23FF.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/2zxvFjm3pvRtHk8EguBsHpQRsJd.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/2AjIpv85kaR8FjwWvgxaanh5gS0.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/4yRpcYTqwYGyQwCL2kbK8edQq3L.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/hF4W40kpeubfK90VrS0gJXXdcMx.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/snmI3AzZ1p1aXLecfgT0EkUQBtu.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-21T11:50:42.012+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Back to the Past","runtime":107,"tagline":"To save tomorrow, they must survive yesterday.","homepage":"https://wellgousa.com/films/back-to-the-past","overview":"In the Qin Dynasty, time-traveller Hong Siu-lung has lived in seclusion with his family for twenty years. Yet every step he takes remains under the watchful eye of his former disciple, now the Qin Emperor. On the brink of ultimate power after conquering the six warring states, the emperor is suddenly ambushed by a mysterious team wielding advanced weapons clearly originating from Hong’s time. Drawn together by fate again, Hong and Qin Emperor are forced to confront the long-buried conflict between them, because the future now depends on how they settle their past."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"寻秦记","runtime":107,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.onecool.com/sc/film/back-to-the-past/","overview":"2030年，香港诸多现代物被抽取到秦朝，抽送中的生命体更是因此灰飞烟灭。拯救行动迫在眉睫，项少龙带领众人孤注一掷。秦王的欲望，家人的安危，是离开还是留下，都将在这秘境之地寻找答案。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"尋秦記","runtime":107,"tagline":"穿越師徒情仇 跨時代天命回歸","homepage":"","overview":"一場多年前的冤獄，引發改變歷史命運的危機！Ken（苗僑偉飾）誓要穿越回秦代稱王，彌補他因冤獄而失去的人生。身在秦朝的項少龍（古天樂飾）一家雖歸隱田園，無奈一舉一動仍被徒弟秦王（林峰飾）盡收眼底；正當秦王以為一統六國，稱霸天下之時竟碰到現代人 Ken 的突襲，他不得不去尋找自己又敬又畏的師傅項少龍。師徒久別二十年終於再次碰面，Ken 的出現也讓三人的命運捆綁，秦朝再起風波，恩怨終須了結。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"尋秦記","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"一場多年前的冤獄，引發改變歷史命運的危機！Ken（苗僑偉 飾）誓要穿越回秦代稱王，彌補他因冤獄而失去的人生。身在秦朝的項少龍（古天樂 飾）一家雖歸隱田園，無奈一舉一動仍被他的徒弟秦王（林峯 飾）盡收眼底；正當秦王以為即將一統六國，稱霸天下之時，竟碰到現代人Ken的突襲，他不得不去尋找自己又敬又畏師傅項少龍。師徒久別二十年終於再次碰面，Ken的出現也讓三人的命運捆綁，秦朝再起風波，多年的恩怨終須了結。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"เจาะเวลาหาจิ๋นซี เดอะมูฟวี่","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ดำเนินเรื่องต่อจากฉบับทีวีซีรีส์ที่ได้รับความนิยมเป็นอย่างมากหลายประเทศในเอเชียรวมทั้งประเทศไทย โดยเรื่องราวฉบับภาพยนตร์จะเล่าผ่านตัวละครคือ เคน นายทหารชาวอเมริกันและเพื่อนร่วมสนามรบอีก 5 นายที่ใช้เครื่องไทม์แมชชีนในการย้อนเวลากลับไปสู่อดีตในสมัยราชวงศ์ฉินเพื่อที่จะเอาชนะกองทัพฉินด้วยยุทโธปกรณ์สมัยใหม่ เมื่อเป็นเช่นนี้ จิ๋นซีฮ่องเต้ จึงทรงมีพระบัญชาให้ เซี่ยงเส้าหลง อดีตนายทหารผู้จงรักภักดีที่ปลีกตัวไปใช้ชีวิตสันโดษให้กลับมารับมือกับวิกฤตการณ์ในครั้งนี้ และด้วยความช่วยเหลือจากหญิงสาวผู้ลึกลับ จึงทำให้เซี่ยงเส้าหลงค้นพบแผนการอันชั่วร้ายที่คาดไม่ถึงของเคนซึ่งยากจะรับมือได้โดยง่าย"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Tầm Tần Ký","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"“TẦM TẦN KÝ” là phim điện ảnh kể về câu chuyện của hơn 20 năm sau, kể từ tập cuối bộ phim truyền hình mang tên Cỗ Máy Thời Gian (tựa phim ở Việt Nam)."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"695aa9a3ed9cd8303bcc99a8","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/695aa9a3ed9cd8303bcc99a8","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$11","created_at":"2026-01-04T17:55:48.005Z","updated_at":"2026-01-04T17:55:48.080Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":7,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":923667,"adult":false,"title":"Twilight of the Warriors: Walled In","video":false,"overview":"In 1980s Hong Kong, troubled youth Chan Lok-kwun, a mainland refugee, struggles to survive in the Kowloon Walled City by joining underground fights. Betrayed by crime boss Mr. Big while trying to buy a fake ID, he steals drugs from him and seeks refuge in the Walled City, where he encounters Cyclone, a compassionate yet authoritative crime lord.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.0995,"vote_count":422,"poster_path":"/h0tunBO4tMjvKVVG7fXqHgwOr5C.jpg","release_date":"2024-05-01","vote_average":7.015,"backdrop_path":"/kK76jqpSI832Ucsx2qDEpxXNtXv.jpg","original_title":"九龍城寨之圍城","original_language":"cn"},{"id":293092,"adult":false,"title":"Back to the USSR","video":false,"overview":"Reima Elo ends up trying to commit suicide when he is abandoned by his wife Molla. He is also the village's laughing stock due to his communism. At a critical moment, a Lenin lookalike from Russia named Vladimir rescues him.","genre_ids":[18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1123,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/bPH1loAZn6VAq8evOjGYFUomJwG.jpg","release_date":"1992-03-27","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Back to the USSR – takaisin Ryssiin","original_language":"fi"},{"id":11324,"adult":false,"title":"Shutter Island","video":false,"overview":"World War II soldier-turned-U.S. Marshal Teddy Daniels investigates the disappearance of a patient from a hospital for the criminally insane, but his efforts are compromised by troubling visions and a mysterious doctor.","genre_ids":[18,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.0553,"vote_count":25436,"poster_path":"/nrmXQ0zcZUL8jFLrakWc90IR8z9.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-14","vote_average":8.2,"backdrop_path":"/8xt8AMb1OKC63AdhNSaYBWxB4Iq.jpg","original_title":"Shutter Island","original_language":"en"},{"id":597,"adult":false,"title":"Titanic","video":false,"overview":"101-year-old Rose DeWitt Bukater tells the story of her life aboard the Titanic, 84 years later. A young Rose boards the ship with her mother and fiancé. Meanwhile, Jack Dawson and Fabrizio De Rossi win third-class tickets aboard the ship. Rose tells the whole story from Titanic's departure through to its death—on its first and last voyage—on April 15, 1912.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":29.5562,"vote_count":26800,"poster_path":"/9xjZS2rlVxm8SFx8kPC3aIGCOYQ.jpg","release_date":"1997-12-18","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/xnHVX37XZEp33hhCbYlQFq7ux1J.jpg","original_title":"Titanic","original_language":"en"},{"id":2786,"adult":false,"title":"Pierrot le Fou","video":false,"overview":"Pierrot escapes his boring society and travels from Paris to the Mediterranean Sea with Marianne, a girl chased by hit-men from Algeria. They lead an unorthodox life, always on the run.","genre_ids":[18,10749,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.779,"vote_count":922,"poster_path":"/i124H6iQB4CawrgFW9aZaZs7OBO.jpg","release_date":"1965-11-05","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/4zJ9w3lZcZI3mBXcNiq6s8bqpDO.jpg","original_title":"Pierrot le fou","original_language":"fr"},{"id":239,"adult":false,"title":"Some Like It Hot","video":false,"overview":"In Prohibition-era Chicago, musicians Joe and Jerry witness a mob hit, and flee the state in an all-female band disguised as Josephine and Daphne, but further complications set in.","genre_ids":[35,10749,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.2986,"vote_count":3783,"poster_path":"/hVIKyTK13AvOGv7ICmJjK44DTzp.jpg","release_date":"1959-03-19","vote_average":8.087,"backdrop_path":"/5zTwAcnI3zCJ0mucPPnoBtkSWEV.jpg","original_title":"Some Like It Hot","original_language":"en"},{"id":62,"adult":false,"title":"2001: A Space Odyssey","video":false,"overview":"Humanity finds a mysterious object buried beneath the lunar surface and sets off to find its origins with the help of HAL 9000, the world's most advanced super computer.","genre_ids":[878,9648,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.0926,"vote_count":12352,"poster_path":"/ve72VxNqjGM69Uky4WTo2bK6rfq.jpg","release_date":"1968-04-02","vote_average":8.1,"backdrop_path":"/w5IDXtifKntw0ajv2co7jFlTQDM.jpg","original_title":"2001: A Space Odyssey","original_language":"en"},{"id":1370,"adult":false,"title":"Rambo III","video":false,"overview":"Combat has taken its toll on Rambo, but he's finally begun to find inner peace in a monastery. When Rambo's friend and mentor Col. Trautman asks for his help on a top secret mission to Afghanistan, Rambo declines but must reconsider when Trautman is captured.","genre_ids":[28,12,53,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.7202,"vote_count":3405,"poster_path":"/uycbt9iVlAnKkQIisqUWuO8hVcm.jpg","release_date":"1988-05-24","vote_average":6.199,"backdrop_path":"/Afkcvov0y7osi6NwubwpPL6pfrA.jpg","original_title":"Rambo III","original_language":"en"},{"id":88,"adult":false,"title":"Dirty Dancing","video":false,"overview":"Expecting the usual tedium that accompanies a summer in the Catskills with her family, 17-year-old Frances 'Baby' Houseman is surprised to find herself stepping into the shoes of a professional hoofer—and unexpectedly falling in love.","genre_ids":[18,10402,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.9247,"vote_count":6418,"poster_path":"/9Jw6jys7q9gjzVX5zm1z0gC8gY9.jpg","release_date":"1987-08-21","vote_average":7.327,"backdrop_path":"/6iDQCBUSZKzY8Rnu8ECwl2gXcfG.jpg","original_title":"Dirty Dancing","original_language":"en"},{"id":13180,"adult":false,"title":"Zeitgeist: Addendum","video":false,"overview":"Zeitgeist: Addendum premiered at the 5th Annual Artivist Film Festival. Director Peter Joseph stated: \"The failure of our world to resolve the issues of war, poverty, and corruption, rests within a gross ignorance about what guides human behavior to begin with. It address the true source of the instability in our society, while offering the only fundamental, long-term solution.\"","genre_ids":[99,36,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5907,"vote_count":255,"poster_path":"/5zlBxoyWRyzPOHO7QmmAC1WG9bK.jpg","release_date":"2008-10-02","vote_average":7.231,"backdrop_path":"/4o1fHunY6UawAjfBsILGyJ1hKvU.jpg","original_title":"Zeitgeist: Addendum","original_language":"en"},{"id":79108,"adult":false,"title":"Starbuck","video":false,"overview":"David Wozniak is a perpetual adolescent who discovers that, as a sperm donor, he has fathered 533 children. He is advised that more than 100 of his offspring are trying to force the fertility clinic to reveal the true identity of \"Starbuck,\" the pseudonym he used when donating his sperm. To make matters worse, his girlfriend Valérie is pregnant with his child, but doesn't feel that he is mature enough to be a father.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.7757,"vote_count":464,"poster_path":"/t7ZyIR941krELzP7POiFUu0yhFq.jpg","release_date":"2011-07-27","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/98SMte6G9hUxLpe2OZuF8UvJkTL.jpg","original_title":"Starbuck","original_language":"fr"},{"id":6844,"adult":false,"title":"The Ten Commandments","video":false,"overview":"Escaping death, a Hebrew infant is raised in a royal household to become a prince. Upon discovery of his true heritage, Moses embarks on a personal quest to reclaim his destiny as the leader and liberator of the Hebrew people.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.8446,"vote_count":1795,"poster_path":"/3Ei59AR64x6dMZfWobPCkZjbqTL.jpg","release_date":"1956-10-05","vote_average":7.768,"backdrop_path":"/2w5jm8aZilHjDTpqP3uQRG8kmeV.jpg","original_title":"The Ten Commandments","original_language":"en"},{"id":4481,"adult":false,"title":"Manon of the Spring","video":false,"overview":"In this, the sequel to Jean de Florette, Manon has grown into a beautiful young shepherdess living in the idyllic Provencal countryside. She plots vengeance on the men who greedily conspired to acquire her father's land years earlier.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9662,"vote_count":554,"poster_path":"/1qpu6Zc1PSDL3UbDNIZJ6YuhJDW.jpg","release_date":"1986-11-19","vote_average":7.581,"backdrop_path":"/3ejcvnHxMFfCbnFi736cXi1ChH1.jpg","original_title":"Manon des sources","original_language":"fr"},{"id":12230,"adult":false,"title":"One Hundred and One Dalmatians","video":false,"overview":"When a litter of dalmatian puppies are abducted by the minions of Cruella De Vil, the parents must find them before she uses them for a diabolical fashion statement.","genre_ids":[12,16,35,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.875,"vote_count":6579,"poster_path":"/kSlYq6FrBUviGSEh8v4L9nrSnBT.jpg","release_date":"1961-01-25","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/cZgUATpU4NDlsfGj7sRriKJEiLB.jpg","original_title":"One Hundred and One Dalmatians","original_language":"en"},{"id":426,"adult":false,"title":"Vertigo","video":false,"overview":"A retired San Francisco detective suffering from acrophobia investigates the strange activities of an old friend's wife, all the while becoming dangerously obsessed with her.","genre_ids":[9648,10749,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.4179,"vote_count":6218,"poster_path":"/15uOEfqBNTVtDUT7hGBVCka0rZz.jpg","release_date":"1958-05-09","vote_average":8.148,"backdrop_path":"/rtVwkTqllcmyY4TVOycgVBHppWf.jpg","original_title":"Vertigo","original_language":"en"},{"id":2108,"adult":false,"title":"The Breakfast Club","video":false,"overview":"Five high school students from different walks of life endure a Saturday detention under a power-hungry principal. The disparate group includes rebel John, princess Claire, outcast Allison, brainy Brian and Andrew, the jock. Each has a chance to tell his or her story, making the others see them a little differently -- and when the day ends, they question whether school will ever be the same.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.2703,"vote_count":8410,"poster_path":"/gp4zlj7wgbiofLMNsTPndMuO3PN.jpg","release_date":"1985-02-15","vote_average":7.725,"backdrop_path":"/kjVgUMsG0PKBXzlP8HGNQpWDxAX.jpg","original_title":"The Breakfast Club","original_language":"en"},{"id":28942,"adult":false,"title":"The Brood","video":false,"overview":"A man tries to uncover an unconventional psychologist's therapy techniques on his institutionalized wife, while a series of brutal attacks committed by a brood of mutant children coincides with the husband's investigation.","genre_ids":[27,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0404,"vote_count":788,"poster_path":"/zSEt4QXRI4Gypd9xvzvucOmPNl5.jpg","release_date":"1979-05-25","vote_average":6.718,"backdrop_path":"/mDr6XaqC9IKA2j35c24cGdc5a0W.jpg","original_title":"The Brood","original_language":"en"},{"id":1667,"adult":false,"title":"March of the Penguins","video":false,"overview":"Every year, thousands of Antarctica's emperor penguins make an astonishing journey to breed their young. They walk, marching day and night in single file 70 miles into the darkest, driest and coldest continent on Earth.  This amazing, true-life tale is touched with humour and alive with thrills. Breathtaking photography captures the transcendent beauty and staggering drama of devoted parent penguins who, in the fierce polar winter, take turns guarding their egg and trekking to the ocean in search of food. Predators hunt them, storms lash them. But the safety of their adorable chicks makes it all worthwhile. So follow the leader... to adventure!!","genre_ids":[99,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0823,"vote_count":1192,"poster_path":"/o9xJ1xG1WKlHkl8ACqq0LShOuMu.jpg","release_date":"2005-01-26","vote_average":7.079,"backdrop_path":"/lPsKI7VR1FJY3w8iEOBZEhWAESc.jpg","original_title":"La Marche de l'empereur","original_language":"fr"},{"id":78,"adult":false,"title":"Blade Runner","video":false,"overview":"In the smog-choked dystopian Los Angeles of 2019, blade runner Rick Deckard is called out of retirement to terminate a quartet of replicants who have escaped to Earth seeking their creator for a way to extend their short life spans.","genre_ids":[878,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.3636,"vote_count":14704,"poster_path":"/63N9uy8nd9j7Eog2axPQ8lbr3Wj.jpg","release_date":"1982-06-25","vote_average":7.94,"backdrop_path":"/hJ5R9d6QuH3tzr8L8neZZTuzNXm.jpg","original_title":"Blade Runner","original_language":"en"},{"id":150540,"adult":false,"title":"Inside Out","video":false,"overview":"When 11-year-old Riley moves to a new city, her Emotions team up to help her through the transition. Joy, Fear, Anger, Disgust and Sadness work together, but when Joy and Sadness get lost, they must journey through unfamiliar places to get back home.","genre_ids":[16,10751,12,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.8246,"vote_count":23174,"poster_path":"/2H1TmgdfNtsKlU9jKdeNyYL5y8T.jpg","release_date":"2015-06-17","vote_average":7.909,"backdrop_path":"/jJKZaTBNenlFclQyjrnvzkRmvWE.jpg","original_title":"Inside Out","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":165,"adult":false,"title":"Back to the Future Part II","video":false,"overview":"Marty and Doc are at it again as the time-traveling duo head to 2015 to nip some McFly family woes in the bud. But things go awry thanks to bully Biff Tannen and a pesky sports almanac. In a last-ditch attempt to set things straight, Marty finds himself bound for 1955 and face to face with his teenage parents -- again.","genre_ids":[12,35,878],"popularity":7.1854,"vote_count":13684,"poster_path":"/YBawEsTkUZBDajKbd5LiHkmMGf.jpg","release_date":"1989-11-22","vote_average":7.775,"backdrop_path":"/w6tPctxWAsHoQXeKxxNOT6lYKpx.jpg","original_title":"Back to the Future Part II","original_language":"en"},{"id":168,"adult":false,"title":"Star Trek IV: The Voyage Home","video":false,"overview":"When a huge alien probe enters the galaxy and begins to vaporize Earth's oceans, Kirk and his crew must travel back in time in order to bring back whales and save the planet.","genre_ids":[878,12],"popularity":3.5483,"vote_count":1612,"poster_path":"/xY5TzGXJOB3L9rhZ1MbbPyVlW5J.jpg","release_date":"1986-11-26","vote_average":7.166,"backdrop_path":"/2LiU13aDAWpU2mX25JdacTzBnyr.jpg","original_title":"Star Trek IV: The Voyage Home","original_language":"en"},{"id":185,"adult":false,"title":"A Clockwork Orange","video":false,"overview":"In a near-future Britain, young Alexander DeLarge and his pals get their kicks beating and raping anyone they please. When not destroying the lives of others, Alex swoons to the music of Beethoven. The state, eager to crack down on juvenile crime, gives an incarcerated Alex the option to undergo an invasive procedure that'll rob him of all personal agency. In a time when conscience is a commodity, can Alex change his tune?","genre_ids":[878,80],"popularity":9.2739,"vote_count":13612,"poster_path":"/4sHeTAp65WrSSuc05nRBKddhBxO.jpg","release_date":"1971-10-28","vote_average":8.18,"backdrop_path":"/nLFxvLokHe3bQmrmAfljIfax2jQ.jpg","original_title":"A Clockwork Orange","original_language":"en"},{"id":196,"adult":false,"title":"Back to the Future Part III","video":false,"overview":"The final installment finds Marty digging the trusty DeLorean out of a mineshaft and looking for Doc in the Wild West of 1885. But when their time machine breaks down, the travelers are stranded in a land of spurs. More problems arise when Doc falls for pretty schoolteacher Clara Clayton, and Marty tangles with Buford Tannen.","genre_ids":[12,35,878],"popularity":6.747,"vote_count":11312,"poster_path":"/crzoVQnMzIrRfHtQw0tLBirNfVg.jpg","release_date":"1990-05-25","vote_average":7.489,"backdrop_path":"/AtF7TESJEMmImBRUj9Z7HmW2ZH0.jpg","original_title":"Back to the Future Part III","original_language":"en"},{"id":947891,"adult":false,"title":"My Old Ass","video":false,"overview":"An 18th birthday mushroom trip brings free-spirited Elliott face-to-face with her wisecracking 39-year-old self. But when Elliott’s \"old ass\" starts handing out warnings about what her younger self should and shouldn't do, Elliott realizes she has to rethink everything about family, love, and what's becoming a transformative summer.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":3.2189,"vote_count":443,"poster_path":"/yUs4Sw9AyTg2sA1qWBkNpD2mGSj.jpg","release_date":"2024-09-13","vote_average":6.801,"backdrop_path":"/iPHsjvbFyGbeCEDC7u8Ib8U1zS6.jpg","original_title":"My Old Ass","original_language":"en"},{"id":1291745,"adult":false,"title":"Kavej","video":false,"overview":"The film shows how we often complicate our own lives and overlook what truly matters. Two friends, Veronika and Klára, return home to a series of family and social gatherings - three weddings and one funeral - that turn their worlds upside down and lead them to discover love, happiness, and their place in life.","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":0.301,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/mXQfajD7gLPxWeEvOJgSfeDPTiV.jpg","release_date":"2024-07-18","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/pNusM7B0Ekz15V6rGRwWk1OCEPN.jpg","original_title":"Kavej","original_language":"sk"},{"id":646,"adult":false,"title":"Dr. No","video":false,"overview":"Agent 007 battles mysterious Dr. No, a scientific genius bent on destroying the U.S. space program. As the countdown to disaster begins, Bond must go to Jamaica, where he encounters beautiful Honey Ryder, to confront a megalomaniacal villain in his massive island headquarters.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":7.2117,"vote_count":3956,"poster_path":"/f9HsemSsBEHN5eoMble1bj6fDxs.jpg","release_date":"1962-10-07","vote_average":6.991,"backdrop_path":"/ptcXbbxTyjHfEE4d4QocNP0YQct.jpg","original_title":"Dr. No","original_language":"en"},{"id":657,"adult":false,"title":"From Russia with Love","video":false,"overview":"Agent 007 is back in the second installment of the James Bond series, this time battling a secret crime organization known as SPECTRE. Russians Rosa Klebb and Kronsteen are out to snatch a decoding device known as the Lektor, using the ravishing Tatiana to lure Bond into helping them. Bond willingly travels to meet Tatiana in Istanbul, where he must rely on his wits to escape with his life in a series of deadly encounters with the enemy.","genre_ids":[28,53,12],"popularity":6.5294,"vote_count":3280,"poster_path":"/zx4V17FP8oclNvOpTgs2iCCtiYk.jpg","release_date":"1963-10-10","vote_average":7.066,"backdrop_path":"/8JMiQa0OqsCYvbNUrQIrMzwV7g2.jpg","original_title":"From Russia with Love","original_language":"en"},{"id":658,"adult":false,"title":"Goldfinger","video":false,"overview":"Special agent 007 comes face to face with one of the most notorious villains of all time, and now he must outwit and outgun the powerful tycoon to prevent him from cashing in on a devious scheme to raid Fort Knox -- and obliterate the world's economy.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":6.2145,"vote_count":3872,"poster_path":"/aKNFzaqQgPzsGXnsMc4kJH5hFIV.jpg","release_date":"1964-09-20","vote_average":7.355,"backdrop_path":"/f1Is9VLQZSRpeLMU7mIcj5aXclt.jpg","original_title":"Goldfinger","original_language":"en"},{"id":662,"adult":false,"title":"La Jetée","video":false,"overview":"A man confronts his past during an experiment that attempts to find a solution to the problems of a post-apocalyptic world caused by a world war.","genre_ids":[18,10749,878],"popularity":3.3202,"vote_count":970,"poster_path":"/elGidsRHXkk8UyrtLbcMhaptDyp.jpg","release_date":"1962-02-16","vote_average":7.883,"backdrop_path":"/3Z2OhNVU0FhxGZJIq6Gn32UNoKu.jpg","original_title":"La Jetée","original_language":"fr"},{"id":667,"adult":false,"title":"You Only Live Twice","video":false,"overview":"A mysterious spacecraft captures Russian and American space capsules and brings the two superpowers to the brink of war. James Bond investigates the case in Japan and comes face to face with his archenemy Blofeld.","genre_ids":[28,53,12],"popularity":7.1355,"vote_count":2402,"poster_path":"/fdRbvRcEXcf2rC4ghLFZzCWPSmB.jpg","release_date":"1967-06-13","vote_average":6.593,"backdrop_path":"/cpZAXIYA0lkZMpAt7d1MmH8ojNV.jpg","original_title":"You Only Live Twice","original_language":"en"},{"id":668,"adult":false,"title":"On Her Majesty's Secret Service","video":false,"overview":"With the help of Marc-Ange Draco, head of the Unione Corse crime syndicate, and Draco's troubled daughter Tracy, James Bond tracks his archnemesis, Ernst Stravro Blofeld, to a mountaintop retreat in the Swiss Alps, where he is training an army of beautiful, lethal women.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":5.3271,"vote_count":2077,"poster_path":"/m3KfbxvqaiAvRJ6MpguA3GuLdDQ.jpg","release_date":"1969-12-18","vote_average":6.562,"backdrop_path":"/58pMrmwwcKamJIdjUlinE6QX1Fs.jpg","original_title":"On Her Majesty's Secret Service","original_language":"en"},{"id":682,"adult":false,"title":"The Man with the Golden Gun","video":false,"overview":"Cool government operative James Bond searches for a stolen invention that can turn the sun's heat into a destructive weapon. He soon crosses paths with the menacing Francisco Scaramanga, a hitman so skilled he has a seven-figure working fee. Bond then joins forces with the swimsuit-clad Mary Goodnight, and together they track Scaramanga to a Thai tropical isle hideout where the killer-for-hire lures the slick spy into a deadly maze for a final duel.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":4.9709,"vote_count":2220,"poster_path":"/xVkbKwGnBVNQ122GN5bCTMyPbWz.jpg","release_date":"1974-12-04","vote_average":6.456,"backdrop_path":"/3tpNEbRahT8smy7RraaWa0xg9Gv.jpg","original_title":"The Man with the Golden Gun","original_language":"en"},{"id":686,"adult":false,"title":"Contact","video":false,"overview":"A radio astronomer receives the first extraterrestrial radio signal ever picked up on Earth. As the world powers scramble to decipher the message and decide upon a course of action, she must make some difficult decisions between her beliefs, the truth, and reality.","genre_ids":[18,878,9648],"popularity":7.0764,"vote_count":4862,"poster_path":"/bCpMIywuNZeWt3i5UMLEIc0VSwM.jpg","release_date":"1997-07-11","vote_average":7.438,"backdrop_path":"/yFkUPqBuUnbhYbQL8VFpTrAT9za.jpg","original_title":"Contact","original_language":"en"},{"id":691,"adult":false,"title":"The Spy Who Loved Me","video":false,"overview":"Russian and British submarines with nuclear missiles on board both vanish from sight without a trace. England and Russia both blame each other as James Bond tries to solve the riddle of the disappearing ships. But the KGB also has an agent on the case.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":5.5757,"vote_count":2166,"poster_path":"/3ZxHKFxMYvAko680DsRgAZKWcLi.jpg","release_date":"1977-07-07","vote_average":6.825,"backdrop_path":"/8lRdfsmJjUXQU3DMOOB3vVIhJxP.jpg","original_title":"The Spy Who Loved Me","original_language":"en"},{"id":696,"adult":false,"title":"Manhattan","video":false,"overview":"Manhattan explores how the life of a middle-aged television writer dating a teenage girl is further complicated when he falls in love with his best friend's mistress.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":3.8199,"vote_count":2566,"poster_path":"/k4eT3EvfxW1L9Wmt04UqJqCvCR6.jpg","release_date":"1979-04-25","vote_average":7.718,"backdrop_path":"/adnSTomHU9YyqV2lx38CgM0UxLS.jpg","original_title":"Manhattan","original_language":"en"},{"id":698,"adult":false,"title":"Moonraker","video":false,"overview":"After Drax Industries' Moonraker space shuttle is hijacked, secret agent James Bond is assigned to investigate, traveling to California to meet the company's owner, the mysterious Hugo Drax. With the help of scientist Dr. Holly Goodhead, Bond soon uncovers Drax's nefarious plans for humanity, all the while fending off an old nemesis, Jaws, and venturing to Venice, Rio, the Amazon...and even outer space.","genre_ids":[28,12,53,878],"popularity":5.3553,"vote_count":2153,"poster_path":"/6LrJdXNmu5uHOVALZxVYd44Lva0.jpg","release_date":"1979-06-26","vote_average":6.182,"backdrop_path":"/mrDC5DLx2wljt4HZGwgkmqlzfcF.jpg","original_title":"Moonraker","original_language":"en"},{"id":750,"adult":false,"title":"Murder She Said","video":false,"overview":"Miss Marple believes she's seen a murder in a passing-by train, yet when the police find no evidence she decides to investigate it on her own.","genre_ids":[35,80,18,9648],"popularity":0.9755,"vote_count":229,"poster_path":"/tqnUJyeirufO0q29PoSPaCpB27E.jpg","release_date":"1961-09-26","vote_average":7.33,"backdrop_path":"/7LAV57poNxNHfDoMq3WslheohbX.jpg","original_title":"Murder She Said","original_language":"en"},{"id":751,"adult":false,"title":"Murder at the Gallop","video":false,"overview":"Miss Marple and Mr. Stringer are witnesses to the death by heart attack of elderly, rich Mr. Enderby. Yet they have their doubts about what happened. The police don't believe them, thus leading Miss Marple to yet again investigate by herself.","genre_ids":[35,80,18,9648,53],"popularity":0.6395,"vote_count":180,"poster_path":"/lCLJ6yutSJc8PkiazcEh8dB6Juh.jpg","release_date":"1963-05-09","vote_average":7.075,"backdrop_path":"/qUInTApfYSwiDYGY89lWqgWc0.jpg","original_title":"Murder at the Gallop","original_language":"en"},{"id":757,"adult":false,"title":"Murder Most Foul","video":false,"overview":"A murderer is brought to court and only Miss Marple is unconvinced of his innocence. Once again she begins her own investigation.","genre_ids":[35,80,18,9648,53],"popularity":1.0422,"vote_count":166,"poster_path":"/qTCKB5rxYzgdWUUH4UMgpRVH3GJ.jpg","release_date":"1964-03-01","vote_average":7.063,"